#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/02_Tutorial_part_2.cfg:191
msgid ""
"First, we will have to deal with the Orcish Grunt stationed in the middle of "
"the river. He should be little trouble."
msgstr ""
"Прво треба да се обрачунамо са оним орковским грокташем, тамо на средини "
"ријеке. Никакав проблем, мишљења сам."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/tutorial/scenarios/02_Tutorial_part_2.cfg:193
msgid ""
"By then, their leader will have recruited more units to send against us and "
"the real fight will begin."
